Package squidpony.squidgrid.mapping

Class MetsaMapFactory

java.lang.Object
squidpony.squidgrid.mapping.MetsaMapFactory
@Beta
public class MetsaMapFactory
extends Object
A map generation factory using Perlin noise to make island chain style maps. Based largely on work done by Metsa from #rgrd
Author:
Eben Howard - http://squidpony.com - howard@squidpony.com
